snippet.textDisplay:
Another Wow Moment for CS10, Mekaal Hassan has shown intelligence from start to finish. 

 Faiz's Poetry is rock solid and it's relevant to this day and age, Mekaal Didn't touch the original melody at all yet turned it into a medley by adding Nabeel's Amazing vocals; Humera Channa is a class apart and Nabeel's voice Compliment the song, Modernized instrumental arrangement of this song and made it apt.

Masterful Job. Loving every bit of it.
